<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79ab7fc5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s3163"><num value="3163">§ 3163.</num><heading> Effect on other laws</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Except as specifically provided for in this subchapter, applicable law shall apply with respect to the authorization and administration of transportation or utility systems.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id79ab7fc6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/487/tXI/s1103">Pub. L. 96–487, title XI, § 1103</ref>, <date date="1980-12-02">Dec. 2, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/2459">94 Stat. 2459</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
